The People of the State of Illinois, Plaintiff-Appellee, v. Eddie Horton, Defendant-Appellant.(No. 58598;First District (5th Division)February 15, 1974.

BARRETT, J., took no part.

James J. Doherty, Public Defender, of Chicago (Harold A. Cowen, Assistant Public Defender, of counsel), for appellant.Bernard Carey, State’s Attorney, of Chicago (Kenneth L. Gillis and Jerald A. Kessler, Assistant State’s Attorneys, of counsel), for the People. PER CURIAM.
